may secret account na nakatago dito,

00:03:15.240 --> 00:03:16.760
pero hindi ko pa nahanap.

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:18.080
hinala ko

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.920
may nakatagong espasyo dito.

